This is Lunarscape one of the recent servers out here. This server is started on march, and released on 23 may. And we are looking for you!
Lunarscape is a Pre-EOC server, we have all the skills working and is eco. Skills are not fast but not to slow either. We have squeel of fortune, staking, Queen black dragon, Nex, Dungeoneering, pk points, And hell alot more!
Let the pictures explain why you want to join.
